  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>任務已失效：[resolvedQuestName]</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The bandit camp has packed up and moved on. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>匪徒們已收拾好行裝，離開了這裡。任務[resolvedQuestName]已經失效。</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Payment arrived -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterLabel.slateRef>獎勵已送達</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterLabel.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: You have defeated the bandit camp!\n\nThe payment from [asker_faction_name] has arrived. -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterText.slateRef>你已經擊敗了匪徒營地！\n\n來自[asker_faction_name]的獎勵已經送達。</OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterText.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] -->
